Title: Specification and Verification of a Wavefront Algorithm for the Algebraic Path Problem  
Author: Stephen B. Seidman 
Keyword: Key Words and Phrases: algebraic path problem, wavefront algorithm, systolic algorithm, verification of parallel algorithms  
Web: 68Q22, 68Q60, 65Y05  
Note: MR Subject Classification Numbers:  
Address: Auburn, AL 36849  
Affiliation: Department of Computer Science and Engineering Auburn University  
Abstract: In recent papers, Rice and Seidman have proposed a model of wavefront computation on a general interconnection network and used it to develop a language for specifying wavefront algorithms on an n-dimensional grid of processors. In this paper, the semantics for the language is used to specify and verify a wavefront algorithm for the algebraic path problem. 
